offering $42-a-share in a hostile takover bid for the company, said
it was willing to raise the price tag to $45 a share if USG
negotiates a merger agreement.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
dropped .68 to 147.19. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was down 1.27 at 301.87.
