   Blue-chip issues staged a modest rally, but the
rest of the stock market lagged in a sluggish session Monday.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials rose 10.94 to 2,043.27.
   But declining issues outnumbered advances by more than 4 to 3 in
New York Stock Exchange-listed trading, with 617 up, 875 down and
